overview: Arina does it better  So Arina Hashimoto won the 2018 best JAV actress award, which is pretty neat. I for one, welcome our new JAV overlord. She had a very solid year, her acting did indeed improve greatly and she is one of the most beautiful girls in the industry right now. Plus she has those Arina legs, which are the best.
title: All Nude Arina Hashimoto
